{
  "page": "Womb of the World",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Essos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Womb of the World is located in Essos\"><img alt=\"Womb of the World is located in Essos\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/300px-Essos.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/450px-Essos.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/Essos.png/600px-Essos.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 39.4%; left: 89.7%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Womb of the World\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Womb of the World</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a> and the location of the Womb of the World\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Womb of the World</b> is a large lake that lies just west of <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_of_Mountains\" title=\"Mother of Mountains\">Mother of Mountains</a> within the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a> of central <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is a holy place to the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> people.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Geography\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Geography</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Culture\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Culture</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Geography\">Geography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Womb_of_the_World&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Geography\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Zach_Graves_The_Womb_of_the_World.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/Zach_Graves_The_Womb_of_the_World.JPG/350px-Zach_Graves_The_Womb_of_the_World.JPG\" width=\"350\" height=\"228\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/Zach_Graves_The_Womb_of_the_World.JPG/525px-Zach_Graves_The_Womb_of_the_World.JPG 1.5x, /images/d/d2/Zach_Graves_The_Womb_of_the_World.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Zach_Graves_The_Womb_of_the_World.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Womb of the World, by  Zach Graves © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>The Womb of the World has cool and clean waters<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and is surrounded by a fringe of tall reeds.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> believe it has no bottom, though the lake bottom is actually muddy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> A river runs from the lake north through the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_the_Ifequevron\" title=\"Kingdom of the Ifequevron\">Kingdom of the Ifequevron</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Womb_of_the_World&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> legends, the first man emerged from the depths of the Womb of the World, riding on the back of the first <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horse</a> a thousand thousand years ago.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Merchant caravans are allowed to visit the Western Market of <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a> as long as they do not profane the <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_of_Mountains\" title=\"Mother of Mountains\">Mother of Mountains</a> or the Womb of the World.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Womb_of_the_World&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Womb_of_the_World&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Xia_TaptaraFromTheWombReborn.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5c/Xia_TaptaraFromTheWombReborn.jpg/350px-Xia_TaptaraFromTheWombReborn.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/5/5c/Xia_TaptaraFromTheWombReborn.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Xia_TaptaraFromTheWombReborn.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> at the Womb of the World, by Xia Taptara © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>After eating the <a href=\"/index.php/Stallion_heart\" title=\"Stallion heart\">heart of a stallion</a> as part of a ceremony for <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaego\" title=\"Rhaego\">her child</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> rides to the lake and bathes naked to remove the blood. Afterwards she has sex with Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a> on the grassy shore.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Womb_of_the_World&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Within the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Undying\" title=\"House of the Undying\">House of the Undying</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>, Daenerys has a vision of a line of naked <a href=\"/index.php/Dosh_khaleen\" title=\"Dosh khaleen\">crones</a> creeping from a great lake beneath the <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_of_Mountains\" title=\"Mother of Mountains\">Mother of Mountains</a> and kneeling before her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Womb_of_the_World&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>They rode to the lake the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> called the Womb of the World, surrounded by a fringe of reeds, its water still and calm. A thousand thousand years ago, <a href=\"/index.php/Jhiqui\" title=\"Jhiqui\">Jhiqui</a> told her, the first man had emerged from its depths, riding upon the back of the first <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horse</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Dany cupped her fingers and lifted the sacred waters over her head, cleansing herself and <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaego\" title=\"Rhaego\">the child</a> inside her while <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">the khal</a> and the others looked on.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Remember, Drogo. Remember our first ride together, <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Drogo_and_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Wedding of Drogo and Daenerys Targaryen\">the day we wed</a>. Remember the night we made <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaego\" title=\"Rhaego\">Rhaego</a>, with the <a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a> all around us and your eyes on my face. Remember how cool and clean the water was in the Womb of the World. Remember, my sun-and-stars. Remember, and come back to me.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Womb_of_the_World&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafcentral_essos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Central Essos.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\">2.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\">2.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\">2.7</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_68\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 68\">Chapter 68</a>, Daenerys IX.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_48\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 48\">Chapter 48</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403092500\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.085 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.095 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1507/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12842/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8770/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3091/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4419/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   60.816      1 -total\n 51.69%   31.433     13 Template:Ref\n 32.41%   19.711      1 Template:Location_map\n 30.71%   18.677      1 Template:Location_map+\n 30.23%   18.383     13 Template:Ref/core\n 21.83%   13.275      1 Template:Location_map~\n 12.73%    7.740      3 Template:Quote\n 10.82%    6.583      1 Template:References\n 10.68%    6.495     22 Template:Location_map_Essos\n  2.85%    1.734      3 Template:Location_map/decdeg\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:3187-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403092500 and revision id 326820\n -->\n",
